TextEng: I am in service to Aribeth and the city guard.
Text: 아리베스와 도시 경비대를 위해 일하고 있습니다.

TextEng: Me works for Aribeth and city guard.
Text: 나 아리베스 경이랑 도시 경비 위해 일해.

TextEng: Goodbye.
Me want to know about different city areas.
Text: 나 도시 다른 구역들 알고 싶어.

TextEng: What do you know of the plague?
I need infomation about Neverwinter.
Have you heard of anything odd? Any rumors?
Text: 이상한 소문 같은 거 들은 적 있으세요?

TextEng: You know anything about bad plague?
Text: 나 나쁜 역병에 대해 아는 거 있어?

TextEng: Me wants information about Neverwinter.
Maybe you hear about odd stuff or rumors?
What do you know about attempts at a cure?
Text: 치료제를 찾으려는 시도에 대해 뭘 아시나요?

TextEng: You know about cure attempts maybe?
Text: 치료 시도에 대해 아는 거 있나?

TextEng: I want to ask something else.
Me ask different questions.
What are the different areas of the city?
Tell me about the Beggar's Nest.
Tell me about the Docks district.
Tell me about the Blacklake district.
Tell me about the Peninsula district.
What do you know about the leaders of Neverwinter?
Who run this place? You know about them?
Text: 여긴 누가 다스려? 걔네에 대해 알아?

TextEng: Tell me about the City Core.
I just need to ask a few questions.
Me just wants ask few questions.
Don't question me. I go where I want.
Text: 제게 뭐라 하지 마세요. 전 가고 싶은 곳에 갑니다.

TextEng: You shut up. Me goes where me want.
Text: 닥쳐. 나 가고 싶은 데로 가.

TextEng: I will leave.
Me leave.
You tells about City Core.
You tells about Beggar's Nest.
You tells about Docks district.
You tells about Blacklake district.
You tells about Peninsula district.
Back to the other areas.
Back to other areas?
How has Lord Nasher dealt with the plague?
Lord Nasher do stuff once plague happen?
Text: 나셰르 영주, 역병 터지자 뭐 했어?

TextEng: How has Lady Aribeth dealt with the plague?
What Lady Aribeth do when plague happen?
Text: 아리베스 경, 역병 터지자 뭐 했어?

TextEng: Actually, I'm here about gold.
Me here for gold, actually.
<StartCheck>[Lie]</Start> I'm collecting to fund plague relief. Will you do your duty?
Text: <StartCheck>[거짓말]</Start> 역병 구호 기금을 모금하고 있어요. 의무를 다하시겠어요?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Lie]</Start> Me collect for sick guys. You pay because you nice?
Text: <StartCheck>[거짓말]</Start> 나 아픈 사람들 위해 모아. 너 착하니까 줄래?

TextEng: You give me gold and I leave without killing you!
You give gold to make me go without smashing yous!
Text: 금 주면 너 때리지 않고 갈게!

TextEng: Actually, I don't need anything except the answers to some questions.
Text: 사실 질문에 대한 답 말고는 필요한 게 없어요.

TextEng: Maybe me just need answers to questions.
Then no one will miss you! Pay or die!
Text: 그럼 아무도 당신을 그리워하지 않겠네요! 돈 내거나 죽거나!

TextEng: Nobody miss you, nobody, so you better pay or get squashed!
Text: 아무도 너 안 그리워해, 아무도 안 그래. 그러니 돈 내거나 으스러지거나!

TextEng: I am sorry. I didn't mean to scare you.
Me sorry. Me not mean it.
Text: 나 미안해. 나 그럴 의도 아니었어.
